<p>A brilliant start for West Brom as Callum Robinson puts them ahead after just three minutes. Disappointing defending from Chelsea. </p>

<p>The game is underway at The Hawthorns.</p>

<p>The players are out on the pitch with kick-off rapidly approaching. Can West Brom secure a surprise victory or will Chelsea prevail?</p>

